quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  12,5,"[Ben makko] maaki: \"Ko an yo …ìinngel am, wata a fillano musi…ó…ìe maa …ìen koy…óol maa ngol sakko …ìe fewjane feere; pellet seytaane ko ga√±oAade …ìanngu…óo"
  12,6,"Ko wano nii Joomi maa su…ìoray maa, O anndine firo koy…ói, O timmina neema Makko on e maa…óa e …ìeynguure Yaaquuba nden, wano O timminirnoo mo e baabiraa…ìe maa …ìen …ói…óo: Ibraahiima e ishaaqa. Pellet Joomi maa ko Anndu…óo √ëee√±u…óo"
  12,7,"Gom…óii wonii e Yuusufa e musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen, taskuyeeji wonannde lanndotoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,8,"tuma nde …ìe wi'unoo: \"Pellet ko Yuusufa e neene-gooto mun on …ìuraa yi…óeede ka ben-men dii enen, enen le ko en jamaa …óuu…óu…ìe. Pellet ben-men wonii e majjere …ìanngunde"
  12,9,"Waree Yuusufa maa fero…óon mo e leydi; yeeso ben mon ngon heeranoo on, wonton …ìaawo …óum yim…ìe mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe"
  12,10,"Gooto e ma…ì…ìe wi'i: \"Wata on waru Yuusufa, weddee mo ka ni…ìe woyndu yoga e setee…ìe hoccay mo, si on laatike glloo…ìe"
  12,11,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben amen, ko he…ìu-maa a hoolotaako men e fii Yuusufa? Menen le ko men laa…ìam…ìe mo reedu"
  12,12,"Accitidu-mo e amen o √±aama, o fija. Menen ko men reenoo…ìe mo"
  12,13,"O maaki: \"Min no suninay lam nde yahdoton e makko; mi…óo huli nde boyeeru ndu √±aamata-mo ka welsindi-…óon e makko"
  12,14,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Pellet si saafaandu √±aamii mo e hoore ko men jamaa …óuu…óu…ìe, haray ko men hayru…ìe"
